OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783981082
OL,3,CLabrador rescued from Ben Nevis after
OL,4,Ceating suspected cannabis on hike
OL,6,FRescue volunteers saved a black
OL,7,FLabrador after it had eaten suspected
OL,8,Fcannabis discarded on a hiking trail
OL,9,Fon Ben Nevis earlier this month.
OL,11,FDog trainer Christina Bluhme said she
OL,12,Fwas walking with her dog, Tokyo,
OL,13,Fduring a weekend trip to Scotland in
OL,14,Fearly July when the Labrador became
OL,15,F"critically ill," lost the use of both
OL,16,Fher legs and drifted in and out of
OL,17,Fconsciousness.
OL,19,F"I genuinely thought I was going to
OL,20,Flose her," Christina said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
