OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783981082
OL,3,CLabrador rescued from Ben Nevis after
OL,4,Ceating suspected cannabis on hike
OL,6,FThankfully, Lochaber Mountain Rescue
OL,7,Fcame to save the day and carried Tokyo
OL,8,Fto safety where she was taken to Crown
OL,9,FVets.
OL,11,FVets said the Labrador, who was
OL,12,Fdescribed by the rescue team as a "fit
OL,13,Fand active working dog", had
OL,14,Fsupposedly eaten cannabis that had
OL,15,Fbeen left on the mountain trail, which
OL,16,Fcan be poisonous to some animals.
OL,18,FTHC, the compound found in cannabis,
OL,19,Fis extremely toxic to dogs, due to
OL,20,Ftheir brains having higher cannabinoid
OL,21,Freceptors compared to humans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783981082
OL,3,CLabrador rescued from Ben Nevis after
OL,4,Ceating suspected cannabis on hike
OL,6,FThis means even the smallest amount of
OL,7,Fcannabis can dramatically impact their
OL,8,Fhealth.
OL,10,FAccording to the Vets Now website,
OL,11,Fsymptoms of cannabis intoxication
OL,12,Foccur two hours after ingestion and
OL,13,Finclude vomiting, glassy eyes, and, in
OL,14,Fsome cases, seizures and even a coma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
