FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783981082
OL,3,CLabrador rescued from Ben Nevis after
OL,4,Ceating suspected cannabis on hike
OL,6,FMiss Bluhme expressed her heartfelt
OL,7,Fthanks to the team of volunteers and
OL,8,Fvets who saved her pooch, adding:
OL,9,F"Carrying a 25 kg Labrador down Ben
OL,10,FNevis was impossible on my own, and
OL,11,Ftheir kindness, professionalism and
OL,12,Fcalm support meant everything during
OL,13,Fone of the most frightening days I've
OL,14,Fever experienced."
OL,16,FShe also warned other walkers of the
OL,17,Fdangers of discarded drugs and the
OL,18,Fharm this can cause to dogs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
