PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783981082
OL,3,CLabrador rescued from Ben Nevis after
OL,4,Ceating suspected cannabis on hike
OL,6,FShe said: "Please be aware that
OL,7,Fdiscarded drugs and other toxic
OL,8,Fsubstances can sometimes be found even
OL,9,Fin the most beautiful outdoor places.
OL,10,FIt was something I never imagined we
OL,11,Fwould encounter."
OL,13,FOwners are encouraged to call the
OL,14,Femergency vets immediately if they
OL,15,Fsuspect their pet has cannabis
OL,16,Fpoisoning.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
